      "text": "それでも諦めずにマネジメントを続ける根性は\n素直に凄いと思いますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even so‚ I honestly admire your perseverance\nin continuing to manage without giving up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
