      "text": "とはいえ、まだまだ至らないところだらけですけどね\nもう少し腕を上げてもらわないと困ります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ there are still a lot of things you're not good at‚\nbut you'll need to get a little better at it.",
        "id": ""
